#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an10.197"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an10.197:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 10 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 10 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.197:0.2"
msgid "19. Ariyamaggavagga "
msgstr "19. The Noble Path "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an10.197:0.3"
msgid "197. Anussaritabbasutta "
msgstr "197. Should Be Recollected "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an10.197:1.1"
msgid "“Anussaritabbañca vo, bhikkhave, dhammaṃ desessāmi nānussaritabbañca. "
msgstr "“I will teach you the principle to recollect and the principle not to recollect. … "

msgctxt "an10.197:1.2"
msgid "Taṃ suṇātha … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an10.197:1.3"
msgid "katamo ca, bhikkhave, nānussaritabbo dhammo? "
msgstr "And what is the principle not to recollect? "

msgctxt "an10.197:1.4"
msgid "Pāṇātipāto … pe … "
msgstr "Killing living creatures … "

msgctxt "an10.197:1.5"
msgid "micchādiṭṭhi—"
msgstr "wrong view. "

msgctxt "an10.197:1.6"
msgid "ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, nānussaritabbo dhammo. "
msgstr "This is called the principle not to recollect. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an10.197:2.1"
msgid "Katamo ca, bhikkhave, anussaritabbo dhammo? "
msgstr "And what is the principle to recollect? "

msgctxt "an10.197:2.2"
msgid "Pāṇātipātā veramaṇī … pe … "
msgstr "Not killing living creatures … "

msgctxt "an10.197:2.3"
msgid "sammādiṭṭhi—"
msgstr "right view. "

msgctxt "an10.197:2.4"
msgid "ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, anussaritabbo dhammo”ti. "
msgstr "This is called the principle to recollect.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.197:2.5"
msgid "Navamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
